Description: Provides access to maritime ecosystem data and model outputs from 
    Atlantic Canada. Includes oceanographic indices, species abundance data, 
    and environmental time series. The package wrangles data into standardized 
    formats and provides visualization functions to support ecosystem approach 
    to fisheries management.
